    "This is also reflected in increasing guidance by the United States Food and Drug Administration (FDA) on the use of such models and trials in submissions [55,56], and the European Union REACH (Registration, Evaluation, Authorization, and Restriction of Chemicals) legislation's goal of reducing animal testing by embracing in silico methods [57].",
